// 繝壹・繧ｸ隱ｭ縺ｿ霎ｼ縺ｿ譎ゅ↓チEΔ足跡を追加 (Firebase未接続時のみ表示されめE
// Firebase謗･邯壹′あれば、E.5秒以冁E↓updateFootprintListで上書きされる
setTimeout(() => {
  if (footprints.length === 0) {
    DEMO_FOOTPRINTS.forEach((d, i) => {
      setTimeout(() => {
        footprints.push(new Footprint({ ...d, createdAt: new Date() }));
      }, i * 150);
    });
  }
}, 500);

// 諠・勹莨晁ｪｬ繧貞ｸｸ縺ｫ豬ｮ驕翫＆縺帙ｋ (蜈ｨ諠・勹縺九ｉ6縲・蛟九ｒ繝ｩ繝ｳ繝繝驕ｸ謚槭∵凾縲・・繧梧崛縺・
function spawnSceneLegends(count = 7) {
  // 譌｢蟄倥・莨晁ｪｬ繧貞炎髯､
  footprints = footprints.filter(f => !f.isLegend);
  // 繝ｩ繝ｳ繝ムに選んで追加
  const shuffled = [...SCENE_LEGENDS].sort(() => Math.random() - 0.5);
  const picks = shuffled.slice(0, count);
  picks.forEach((d, i) => {
    setTimeout(() => {
      const fp = new Footprint({ ...d, author: null, createdAt: new Date() });
      fp.isLegend = true; // 莨晁ｪｬ繝槭・繧ｫ繝ｼ (濶ｲ蛻・￠逕ｨ)
      footprints.push(fp);
    }, i * 400);
  });
}
setTimeout(() => spawnSceneLegends(7), 2000);
// 2蛻・ｯ弱↓莨晁ｪｬ繧貞・繧梧崛縺・(鬟ｽ縺阪↑縺・ｈ縺・↓)
setInterval(() => spawnSceneLegends(7), 120000);

// 繝励Οローグは OK 繝懊ち繝ｳ謚ｼ荳九∪で自動起動しなぁE・// 初期状態では brand-mark + OK ボタンのみ表示 (CSS の fadeUp 繧｢繝九Γで頁E↓現れる)、E// runPrologue() は:
//   - 縲悟ｺ冗ｫ縺ｫ謌ｻ繧九阪・繧ｿ繝ｳ謚ｼ荳区凾
//   - OK ボタン押下征E(繝・く繧ｹ繝域ｼ泌・繧貞性繧√◆繝輔Ν再生)
// 縺ｮ縺・★繧後°縺ｧ蜻ｼ縺ｰ繧後ｋ縲・// selectScene(0, true) 縺ｯ蜻ｼ縺ｰ縺ｪ縺・窶・譛蛻昴・菴輔ｂ驕ｸ縺ｰ繧後※ぁE↑ぁE
setTimeout(() => setupWindows(0), 1000);
requestAnimationFrame(loop);

// ============ 蛻晏屓險ｪ蝠剰・愛螳・(繧ｷ繝ｼ繝ｳ繝｡繝九Ηーで誘導グロー) ============
(function() {
  const KEY = 'hmix_theater_visited_v1';
  const hasVisited = (function() {
    try { return localStorage.getItem(KEY) === '1'; } catch(e) { return false; }
  })();
  if (!hasVisited) {
    // 蛻晏屓險ｪ蝠・竊・繧ｷ繝ｼ繝ｳ繝｡繝九Ηーにグロー + 譯亥・繝・く繧ｹ繝・
document.body.classList.add('first-visit');
  }
  // 繧ｷ繝ｼ繝ｳ驕ｸ謚樊凾縺ｫ繝輔Λ繧ｰ繧堤ｫ九※縺ｦ隱伜ｰ弱ｒ豁｢繧√ｋ
  const _origSelectSceneForFirstVisit = selectScene;
  selectScene = function(index, updateTrack) {
    if (document.body.classList.contains('first-visit') && updateTrack !== false) {
      document.body.classList.remove('first-visit');
      try { localStorage.setItem(KEY, '1'); } catch(e) {}
    }
    return _origSelectSceneForFirstVisit.apply(this, arguments);
  };
})();

// ============ tracks.js ロード失敗時の可視フォールバック ============
// tracks.js 縺瑚ｪｭ縺ｿ霎ｼ繧√※ぁE↑ぁE(TRACKS が定義されてぁE↑ぁE 蝣ｴ蜷医・撕縺九↓螢翫ｌ繧九・繧帝亟縺・
setTimeout(() => {
  if (typeof TRACKS === 'undefined' || !Array.isArray(TRACKS) || TRACKS.length === 0) {
    const banner = document.createElement('div');
    banner.setAttribute('role', 'alert');
    banner.style.cssText = `
      position: fixed; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      z-index: 100000; max-width: 480px; padding: 26px 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(12,22,32,0.92), rgba(18,36,48,0.95));
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 164, 76, 0.6);
      border-radius: 12px;
      color: #f5f0e6; font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      text-align: center; line-height: 1.9;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 0 40px rgba(212,164,76,0.2);
    `;
    banner.innerHTML = `
      <div style="color:#f5d896; letter-spacing:0.25em; font-size:11px; margin-bottom:10px;">CONNECTION ERROR</div>
      <div style="font-size:15px; margin-bottom:14px;">讌ｽ譖ｲ繝・・繧ｿ繧定ｪｭ縺ｿ霎ｼ繧√∪縺帙ｓ縺ｧ縺励◆、E/div>
      <div style="font-size:12px; color:rgba(245,240,230,0.7); margin-bottom:18px;">
        繝阪ャ繝域磁邯壹ｒ縺皮｢ｺ隱阪・荳翫√・繝ｼ繧ｸ繧貞・隱ｭ縺ｿ霎ｼ縺ｿ縺励※縺上□さい、E      </div>
      <button onclick="location.reload()" style="
        padding: 10px 26px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212,164,76,0.85), rgba(64,206,180,0.7));
        border: 1px solid rgba(245,216,150,0.6); color: #0a0f0c; border-radius: 6px;
        cursor: pointer;">再読み込み</button>
    `;
    document.body.appendChild(banner);
  }
}, 3000);

// 縲悟ｺ冗ｫ縺ｫ謌ｻ繧九阪・繧ｿ繝ｳ
(function() {
  const btn = $('prologueReturnBtn');
  if (!btn) return;
  btn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    e.stopPropagation();   // 念のためバブル停止 (旧 skip 繝上Φドラ残留対筁E
    runPrologue();
  });
})();

// 自動波紁E(逕ｻ髱｢縺ｮ縺ｩ縺薙°縺ｫ譎よ釜縲√＆繧翫￡縺ｪ縺・
(function autoRipples() {
  function pickPosition() {
    // UI蟇・寔繧ｾ繝ｼ繝ｳ繧帝∩ける: 左 (繧ｷ繝ｼ繝ｳ荳覧) / 右 (アクションタワー) / 丁E(繝励Ξイヤー)
    // 荳ｭ螟ｮ蟇・ｊ 30、E0% 縺ｮ遽・峇縺ｫ繝ｩ繝ｳ繝ム配置
    const x = innerWidth  * (0.25 + Math.random() * 0.5);
    const y = innerHeight * (0.18 + Math.random() * 0.5);
    return { x, y };
  }
  function spawn() {
    // 繝｢繝ｼ繝繝ｫ螻暮幕荳ｭ繝ｻ豐｡蜈･繧｢繧､繝峨Ν中は控える
    const skipWhen = document.body.classList.contains('rings-open')
                  || document.body.classList.contains('ui-idle')
                  || document.querySelector('.license-modal.visible, .footprint-form-modal.visible, .confirm-modal.visible');
    if (!skipWhen && typeof spawnRipple === 'function') {
      const { x, y } = pickPosition();
      spawnRipple(x, y);
    }
    schedule();
  }
  function schedule() {
    // 12、E2秒間隔で1蝗槭∝ｰ代↑めE
setTimeout(spawn, 12000 + Math.random() * 10000);
  }
  schedule();
})();

// ============ ウェルカム音楽: 縲後°縺懊・縺薙∴、E============
const WELCOME_TRACK_ID = 'o2';
let _welcomeMode = true;  // 繧ｷ繝ｼ繝ｳ譛ｪ驕ｸ謚槭・髢薙・ true (ウェルカム音楽ルーチE

function _showAutoplayHint() {
  if (document.getElementById('autoplayHint')) return;
  const hint = document.createElement('div');
  hint.id = 'autoplayHint';
  hint.setAttribute('role', 'status');
  hint.style.cssText = `
    position: fixed; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    z-index: 9999; padding: 18px 30px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(12,22,32,0.85), rgba(18,36,48,0.9));
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,216,150,0.5);
    border-radius: 14px;
    color: #f5f0e6; font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 0 30px rgba(212,164,76,0.18);
    pointer-events: none; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.6s ease;
  `;
  hint.innerHTML = `
    <div style="color:#f5d896; font-family:'Cinzel',serif; letter-spacing:0.3em; font-size:10px; margin-bottom:6px;">
      TAP TO BEGIN
    </div>
    <div>逕ｻ髱｢繧偵ち繝・・縺励※縲∵羅繧貞ｧ九ａ縺ｦ縺上□さい</div>
  `;
  document.body.appendChild(hint);
  requestAnimationFrame(() => { hint.style.opacity = '1'; });
}
function _hideAutoplayHint() {
  const hint = document.getElementById('autoplayHint');
  if (!hint) return;
  hint.style.opacity = '0';
  setTimeout(() => hint.remove(), 800);
}

// ウェルカム曲フェードイン管琁E
let _welcomeFadeTimer = null;
function _welcomeFadeIn(targetVol, durationMs) {
  if (_welcomeFadeTimer) { clearInterval(_welcomeFadeTimer); _welcomeFadeTimer = null; }
  const stepMs = 60;
  const steps = Math.max(1, Math.floor(durationMs / stepMs));
  let i = 0;
  audio.volume = 0;
  _welcomeFadeTimer = setInterval(() => {
    i++;
    // ease-in-out (slow start, accelerate mid, slow end) で自然なフェーチE
const t = i / steps;
    const eased = t < 0.5 ? 2 * t * t : 1 - Math.pow(-2 * t + 2, 2) / 2;
    audio.volume = Math.min(targetVol, targetVol * eased);
    if (i >= steps) {
      audio.volume = targetVol;
      clearInterval(_welcomeFadeTimer);
      _welcomeFadeTimer = null;
    }
  }, stepMs);
}

function _playWelcomeMusic() {
  if (typeof TRACKS === 'undefined') return false;
  const t = TRACKS.find(x => x.id === WELCOME_TRACK_ID);
  if (!t) return false;
  currentTrackData = t;
  trackName.textContent = t.title || '';
  imName.textContent = t.title || '';

  // 履歴に記録 (逶ｴ蜑阪′蜷後§譖ｲ縺ｪ繧蛾㍾隍・＆縺帙↑ぁE 繝ｫ繝ｼ繝怜・逕滓凾縺ｮ閧･螟ｧ蛹夜亟豁｢)
  if (typeof _recordPlay === 'function') {
    const head = (typeof _history !== 'undefined') ? _history[_historyCursor] : null;
    if (!head || !head.track || head.track.id !== t.id) {
      _recordPlay(t, -1, null);
    }
  }

  audio.src = resolveTrackUrl(t);
  audio.load();
  initAudioAnalyser();
  if (audioCtx && audioCtx.state === 'suspended') audioCtx.resume().catch(() => {});

  // 蜀咲函蜑阪↓音量を 0 縺ｫ關ｽ縺ｨ縺励※おく (フェードイン準備)
  const slider = document.getElementById('volumeSlider');
  const savedMute = audio.muted;
  const targetVol = savedMute ? 0 : (slider ? parseInt(slider.value, 10) / 100 : 0.8);
  audio.volume = 0;

  audio.play().then(() => {
    // 7遘偵°縺代※めE▲くりフェードイン (詩皁E↑入場)
    if (!savedMute) _welcomeFadeIn(targetVol, 7000);
  }).catch(() => {
    // Autoplay 繝悶Ο繝・け譎・ 蜿ｯ隕悶ヲ繝ｳ繝医ｒ蜃ｺ縺励※縲∝・蝗槭Θーザー操作で再試衁E    _showAutoplayHint();
    const unlock = () => {
      audio.volume = 0;
      audio.play().then(() => {
        _hideAutoplayHint();
        if (!savedMute) _welcomeFadeIn(targetVol, 7000);
      }).catch(() => {});
      if (audioCtx && audioCtx.state === 'suspended') audioCtx.resume().catch(() => {});
      document.removeEventListener('click', unlock, true);
      document.removeEventListener('keydown', unlock, true);
      document.removeEventListener('touchstart', unlock, true);
    };
    document.addEventListener('click', unlock, true);
    document.addEventListener('keydown', unlock, true);
    document.addEventListener('touchstart', unlock, true);
  });
  if (typeof updateFavButtonState === 'function') updateFavButtonState();
  return true;
}

// 繧ｷ繝ｼ繝ｳ縺碁∈縺ｰ繧後◆らウェルカムモードを抜けめE(selectScene 縺ｮ繝ｩ繝・・)
(function() {
  const _origSelectScene = selectScene;
  selectScene = function(index, updateTrack) {
    if (_welcomeMode && updateTrack !== false) _welcomeMode = false;
    return _origSelectScene.apply(this, arguments);
  };
})();

// ============ 繝励Οローグ入場ボタン ============
// 縲交沐・縺薙・蜈医・浹縺梧ｵ√ｌ縺ｾ縺吶肴款荳・= 入場
//   1) OK ボタンと audio-notice 縺縺第ｶ医☆ (prologue 譛ｬ菴薙・谿九☆)
//   2) runPrologue() 縺ｧ繝・く繧ｹ繝域ｼ泌・ + auto-close を開姁E//   3) 繧ｦ繧ｧ繝ｫ繧ｫ繝髻ｳ讌ｽ繧ょ酔譎ゅ↓再生 (user gesture 下で autoplay 成功)
(function() {
  const enterBtn = document.getElementById('prologueEnterBtn');
  if (!enterBtn) return;
  enterBtn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    e.stopPropagation();
    e.preventDefault();
    // 入場ゲーチEIを隠ぁE(prologue 譛ｬ菴薙・谿九＠縲√ユ繧ｭ繧ｹ繝域ｼ泌・縺ｫ蠑輔″継ぐ)
    const wrap = enterBtn.closest('.prologue-enter-wrap');
    if (wrap) {
      wrap.style.transition = 'opacity 0.5s ease';
      wrap.style.opacity = '0';
      setTimeout(() => { wrap.style.display = 'none'; }, 550);
    }
    // 繝励Ο繝ｭ繝ｼ繧ｰ縺ｮ隧ｩ逧・ｼ泌・繧帝幕蟋・
if (typeof runPrologue === 'function') {
      setTimeout(() => runPrologue(), 150);
    }
    // ウェルカム音楽スターチE(user gesture 丁E
    if (typeof _playWelcomeMusic === 'function') {
      setTimeout(_playWelcomeMusic, 200);
    }
  });
})();

// (莉･蜑阪≠縺｣縺溘後←縺薙〒繧ゅけ繝ｪ繝・け縺ｧ髻ｳ讌ｽ髢句ｧ九堺ｿ晞匱縺ｯ謦､蜴ｻ縲・//  OK 繝懊ち繝ｳ縺悟・蝣ｴ繧ｲ繝ｼ繝医〒縺ゅｋ縺ｨ縺・≧ UX 繧呈・遒ｺ縺ｫ縺吶ｋ縲・
</script>

<!-- Firebase 謗･邯壹Δジュール -->
<script type="module">
import { initializeApp } from 'https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.14.1/firebase-app.js';
import {
  getFirestore, collection, addDoc, query, orderBy, limit, where,
  onSnapshot, serverTimestamp, doc, updateDoc, increment
} from 'https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.14.1/firebase-firestore.js';

const firebaseConfig = {
  apiKey: "AIzaSyBczT5L6PRDJOVAGy3DQ61l-UFbAqI6ESg",
  authDomain: "hmix-footprints.firebaseapp.com",
  projectId: "hmix-footprints",
  storageBucket: "hmix-footprints.firebasestorage.app",
  messagingSenderId: "477684733173",
  appId: "1:477684733173:web:ae0d0986a92a426b08e1bc"
};

const app = initializeApp(firebaseConfig);
const db = getFirestore(app);

// 邁｡譏薙ワ繝・す繝･ (IP縺ｮ莉｣譖ｿ縺ｨ縺励※ブラウザ固有ID)
function getClientHash() {
  let id = localStorage.getItem('hmix_client_id');
  if (!id) {
    id = (crypto.randomUUID ? crypto.randomUUID() : Math.random().toString(36) + Date.now().toString(36));
    localStorage.setItem('hmix_client_id', id);
  }
  return id;
}

// 謚慕ｨｿ繧帝∽ｿ｡
window.fbSubmitFootprint = async function(data) {
  const docData = {
    message: data.message,
    author: data.author,  // null or string
    sceneId: data.sceneId,
    sceneName: data.sceneName,
    createdAt: serverTimestamp(),
    ipHash: getClientHash(),
    hidden: false,
    reports: 0
  };
  console.log('[footprint] submitting:', docData);
  try {
    const ref = await addDoc(collection(db, 'footprints'), docData);
    console.log('[footprint] submitted successfully, id:', ref.id);
    return ref;
  } catch (e) {
    console.error('[footprint] submit error:', e);
    throw e;
  }
};

// 騾壼ｱ繧帝∽ｿ｡
window.fbReportFootprint = async function(footprintId) {
  if (!footprintId || footprintId.startsWith('demo_')) return; // チEΔ足跡は通報不可
  try {
    await addDoc(collection(db, 'reports'), {
      footprintId: footprintId,
      reason: 'user-report',
      createdAt: serverTimestamp(),
      reporterHash: getClientHash()
    });
    // reports カウンタもインクリメンチE(管琁E・判髱｢逕ｨ)
    // (ルールで update は管琁E・・縺ｿ縺ｪ縺ｮ縺ｧ縲√％繧後・邂｡逅・・□縺大虚縺上ゆｸ般ユーザーはreports菴懈・縺ｮ縺ｿ)
  } catch (e) {
    console.warn('report failed:', e);
  }
};

// リアルタイム購読: 譛新20莉ｶ繧貞叙蠕励”idden=false 縺ｮ繧ゅ・縺ｮ縺ｿ
// onSnapshot 縺ｯ謗･邯壻ｸｭ縺壹▲と動く
try {
  const q = query(
    collection(db, 'footprints'),
    where('hidden', '==', false),
    orderBy('createdAt', 'desc'),
    limit(20)
  );

  onSnapshot(q, snapshot => {
    const items = [];
    snapshot.forEach(docSnap => {
      const d = docSnap.data();
      items.push({
        id: docSnap.id,
        message: d.message,
        author: d.author,
        sceneId: d.sceneId,
        sceneName: d.sceneName,
        createdAt: d.createdAt?.toDate ? d.createdAt.toDate() : new Date()
      });
    });
    console.log('[footprint] snapshot received:', items.length, 'items');
    if (typeof window.updateFootprintList === 'function') {
      window.updateFootprintList(items);
    }
  }, err => {
    console.error('[footprint] snapshot error:', err);
  });
} catch (e) {
  console.warn('Firebase Firestore init failed:', e);
}
</script>

<script>
// Firebase縺九ｉ縺ｮ雜ｳ霍｡繝ｪ繧ｹ繝域峩譁ｰ繧呈里蟄倥・ footprints 驟榊・縺ｫ蜿肴丐
window.updateFootprintList = function(items) {
  // チEΔ足跡をクリア (Firebase謗･邯壽・蜉溘＠縺溘ｉ譛ｬ逡ｪ繝・・繧ｿ縺ｫ蛻・ｊ譖ｿ縺・
  footprints = footprints.filter(f => !f.id.startsWith('demo_'));

  const existingIds = new Set(footprints.map(f => f.id));
  const incomingIds = new Set(items.map(i => i.id));

  // 新しい足跡を追加 (画面右端から登場)
  items.forEach((item, idx) => {
    if (!existingIds.has(item.id)) {
      // 譁ｰ隕乗兜遞ｿ縺ｯ蟆代＠驕・ｻｶ縺輔○て追加 (隍・焚蜷梧凾豬∝・繧帝∩ける)
      setTimeout(() => {
        footprints.push(new Footprint(item));
      }, idx * 200);
    }
  });

  // 削除されぁEhiddenに変更されぁE足跡
  footprints = footprints.filter(f => incomingIds.has(f.id) || f.id.startsWith('demo_'));
};
</script>

</body>
</html>
